  <!-- ④ THE STORY CHAPTER -->
  <section id="story" class="story-section">
    <div class="story-sticky-container">
      <div class="story-bg-grid"></div>
      <div class="story-noise-overlay"></div>
      
      <div class="story-narration-wrapper">
        <div class="story-narration narration-s1">"Day one at Helix Corp. Riya opened the legacy repository. 40,000 lines. No comments. No docs. Just code — ancient, dense, and completely foreign."</div>
        <div class="story-narration narration-s2">"She scrolled. And scrolled. Each function a riddle. Each class a locked room. Four hours in, she had touched nothing, changed nothing, understood nothing."</div>
        <div class="story-narration narration-s3">"And then Anuvaad spoke. Not in code. In language. Riya read it — once, twice. The fog lifted. She finally saw not just what the code did, but why it existed."</div>
        <div class="story-narration narration-s4">"Understanding one function changed everything. She began to see the patterns. The intentions. The decisions made by engineers she'd never meet. Code became a conversation across time."</div>
        <div class="story-narration narration-s5">"By week's end, Riya had refactored three modules, written two new services, and taught the entire team how to read the legacy codebase. Not by memorizing it — by understanding it."</div>
        <div class="story-narration narration-s6">"CODE IS LANGUAGE.<br>ANUVAAD SPEAKS BOTH."</div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="story-visuals-container">
        <!-- Scene 1 -->
        <div class="scene-visual visual-s1">
          <div class="code-terminal">
            <div class="terminal-header">
              <span class="dot red"></span>
              <span class="dot yellow"></span>
              <span class="dot green"></span>
              <span class="terminal-title">legacy_module.py</span>
            </div>
            <div class="terminal-body">
              <div class="code-line-typing"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Scene 2 -->
        <div class="scene-visual visual-s2">
          <div class="tunnel-container">
            <div class="tunnel-plane tunnel-left">
              <span>class APIConnector:</span>
              <span>def run_thread(s):</span>
              <span>import sys, os</span>
              <span>sys.setrecursionlimit(5000)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tunnel-plane tunnel-right">
              <span>def hash_pass(p):</span>
              <span>return md5(p)</span>
              <span>db.execute(sql)</span>
              <span>logger.warn("leak")</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tunnel-plane tunnel-top">
              <span>def get_user_meta(u):</span>
              <span>return u.meta_fields</span>
              <span>def validate_sess(s):</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tunnel-plane tunnel-bottom">
              <span>def f(x,l=[]):</span>
              <span>if x in l: return</span>
              <span>l+=[x]</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button class="btn-teaser-translate btn-amber" disabled>TRANSLATING...</button>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Scene 3 -->
        <div class="scene-visual visual-s3">
          <div class="split-layout">
            <div class="split-panel panel-left">
              <div class="panel-header">code</div>
              <div class="panel-content">
                <span class="syn-keyword">def</span> <span class="syn-function">f</span>(x, l=[]):<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="syn-keyword">if</span> x <span class="syn-keyword">in</span> l: <span class="syn-keyword">return</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;l += [x]<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;[<span class="syn-function">f</span>(i, l) <span class="syn-keyword">for</span> i <span class="syn-keyword">in</span> x.<span class="syn-function">__subclasses__</span>()]
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="split-divider"></div>
            <div class="split-panel panel-right">
              <div class="panel-header">english</div>
              <div class="panel-content translation-text"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="aha-overlay">
            <div class="aha-text">Translated.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Scene 4 -->
        <div class="scene-visual visual-s4">
          <div class="ripple-rings-wrapper">
            <svg class="ripple-svg" viewBox="0 0 400 400">
              <circle class="ring ring-1" cx="200" cy="200" r="40" />
              <circle class="ring ring-2" cx="200" cy="200" r="80" />
              <circle class="ring ring-3" cx="200" cy="200" r="120" />
              <circle class="ring ring-4" cx="200" cy="200" r="160" />
            </svg>
            <div class="lang-badge" style="--angle: 0rad; --dist: 40px; --badge-color: #3572A5;">Python</div>
            <div class="lang-badge" style="--angle: 1rad; --dist: 80px; --badge-color: #00ADD8;">Go</div>
            <div class="lang-badge" style="--angle: 2.2rad; --dist: 80px; --badge-color: #b07219;">Java</div>
            <div class="lang-badge" style="--angle: 3.5rad; --dist: 120px; --badge-color: #dea584;">Rust</div>
            <div class="lang-badge" style="--angle: 4.8rad; --dist: 120px; --badge-color: #ffac45;">Swift</div>
            <div class="lang-badge" style="--angle: 5.5rad; --dist: 160px; --badge-color: #A97BFF;">Kotlin</div>
            <div class="lang-badge" style="--angle: 6.1rad; --dist: 160px; --badge-color: #f34b7d;">C++</div>
            
            <div class="stats-ripples">
              <div class="stat-bubble stat-b1"><span>35+</span> languages understood</div>
              <div class="stat-bubble stat-b2"><span>&lt; 3s</span> speed per translation</div>
              <div class="stat-bubble stat-b3"><span>Zero</span> code stored ever</div>
