            <li>
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
              Up to 20 team members
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
              Shared workspace history
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
              Admin billing & controls
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
              Priority 24/7 support
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ⑨ FAQ -->
  <section id="faq" class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal-el" style="text-align: center; margin: 0 auto 64px;">
        <div class="section-badge">FAQ</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Frequently <span>asked questions.</span></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-wrapper reveal-el">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-trigger">
            <h3>What programming languages are supported?</h3>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content">
            <p>Anuvaad supports 35+ languages including Python, JavaScript, TypeScript, Java, C++, C#, Go, Rust, Swift, Kotlin, PHP, Ruby, SQL, HTML, CSS, Dart, Lua, R, Haskell, and more. We add new languages regularly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-trigger">
            <h3>Is my code stored on your servers?</h3>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content">
            <p>No. Your code is processed in real-time by the AI and returned to your browser immediately. We never store code on our servers. Translation history is saved securely in your account database.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-trigger">
            <h3>How accurate are the translations?</h3>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content">
            <p>Anuvaad uses Groq and DeepSeek, which provide highly accurate translations. However, AI translations should always be reviewed before use in production environments.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-trigger">
            <h3>Can I use Anuvaad for free?</h3>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content">
            <p>Yes! The free plan includes 10 translations per day, all 3 modes, and full export capabilities. No credit card required.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-trigger">
            <h3>What's the difference between Free and Pro?</h3>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content">
            <p>Pro gives you unlimited translations, priority processing speed, larger input limits (50K characters), cloud-synced history, and email support.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-trigger">
            <h3>Can I cancel my subscription anytime?</h3>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content">
            <p>Absolutely. You can cancel your Pro subscription at any time. Your access continues until the end of your current billing period. We also offer a 7-day refund policy.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-trigger">
            <h3>How does billing and Razorpay work?</h3>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content">
            <p>Payments are securely processed by Razorpay. You can buy one-off credits or subscribe to the Pro/Team plans using UPI, cards, netbanking, or wallets.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-trigger">
            <h3>Is there a limit on file uploads?</h3>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content">
            <p>Yes, on the Free plan, files are limited to 20KB. The Pro plan supports files up to 200KB for large-scale codebase migrations.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ⑩ FOOTER -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-top">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <h4>Anuvaad<span class="nav-dot">·</span></h4>
          <p>Stop struggling with legacy code. Instantly translate between code, language, and logic.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-nav">
          <div class="footer-nav-col">
